thematic elements

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:09.910 position:56%
and connective tissue throughout the
program, but the other element of it

00:02:09.910 --> 00:02:13.700
that I always like to pay attention
to is what really works musically.

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:16.910
And so when Alban and I, we went
back and forth and back and forth

00:02:16.910 --> 00:02:19.770
and back and forth with
these programs by email,

00:02:19.770 --> 00:02:23.580
