after intuition when, you know,

00:02:36.220 --> 00:02:38.340
everybody can kind
of just get absorbed

00:02:38.340 --> 00:02:40.790
into Bernstein's world there.

00:02:40.790 --> 00:02:43.570
So it was, you know, it was
this combination, I think,

00:02:43.570 --> 00:02:46.540
of trying to have a somewhat
thematic program and also wanting

00:02:46.540 --> 00:02:49.230
to play repertoire that worked.

00:02:49.230 --> 00:02:51.910
OK.

00:02:51.910 --> 00:02:53.890
