00:28:51.360 --> 00:28:56.870
in this world right here having
a conversation truly, and it's,

00:28:56.870 --> 00:28:59.420
there's a lot of trust that has to.

00:28:59.420 --> 00:29:01.920
You know, I think it
probably doesn't hurt

00:29:01.920 --> 00:29:05.430
